These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: lily, zinnia, bellflower, amaryllis, azalea
5 different games are played: domino, poker, chess, go, scrabble
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, davidoff, blend, old-henry, dannemann
The people have 5 different hobbies: magic-tricks, rock-climbing, puzzles, woodworking, dancing
 1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 2. the person playing chess is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 4. the person who growsbellflower is the person who growsbellflower##1
 5. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person playing domino##1
 6. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
 7. the cain-smoker is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
 8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1
10. the person who growslily is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
11. the person who growsazalea is between the davidoff-smoker and the person playing scrabble##2
12. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person playing poker##1
13. the dannemann-smoker is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Flower      | lily        | zinnia | azalea     | bellflower   | amaryllis |
| Game   | chess     | poker      | go | scrabble   | domino    |
| Cigar   | old-henry  | davidoff     | cain | blend | dannemann  |
| Hobby           | rock-climbing | puzzles      | dancing     | woodworking   | magic-tricks     |

