.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
There 5 different types of food: cabbage, tomato, pomegranate, apricot, lime
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: orchid, marigold, azalea, amaryllis, aconite
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, vegafina, cain, tiparillo, bongani
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: soccer, tennis, cycling, snowboarding, skiing
 1. the person who's sport is skiing is in the middle##1
 2. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
 3. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 4. the person eating lime is on the right of the vegafina-smoker##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is between the bluemaster-smoker and the person who growsaconite##2
 6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is the person eating tomato##1
 7. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 8. the cain-smoker is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 9. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
10. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1
11. the cain-smoker is the person eating pomegranate##1
12. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Food         | apricot | cabbage | lime    | tomato  | pomegranate    |
| Flower   | aconite    | marigold       | azalea      | orchid | amaryllis        |
| Cigar   | bongani   | vegafina     | bluemaster    | tiparillo  | cain     |
| Sport     | cycling    | tennis | skiing | snowboarding | soccer |

