.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-3::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: november, april, june, october, february
5 different games are played: mah-jongg, chess, go, domino, poker
There are 5 different favourite colors: blue, turquise, purple, orange, apricot
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: sunflower, daisy, poppy, lily, begonia
 1. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who likes turquise##1
 2. the person who growslily is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes orange is in the middle##1
 4. the person playing mah-jongg is in the middle##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
 7. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 9. the person who likes purple is on the far left##1
10. the person who growssunflower is the person playing domino##1
11. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
12. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who likes apricot##1
13. the person who growsbegonia is between the person playing poker and the person who's birthday is in june##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4       |       5       |
| Birthday         | november | february     | june   | april   | october |
| Game   | poker  | chess | mah-jongg | domino | go        |
| Color   | purple      | turquise      | orange       | apricot       | blue       |
| Flower         | daisy | begonia  | lily    | sunflower    | poppy        |

