.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-4::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: azure, turquise, orange, mauve, aquamarine
House: colonial, townhouse, futuristic, cape-cod, craftsman
The people have 5 different jobs:  manager, librarian, designer, nurse, mechanic
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: action, scientific, documentary, horror, adventure
 1. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
 2. the colonial house is on the right of the librarian##1
 3. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is between the nurse and the person who likes mauve##2
 5. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the futuristic house##1
 6. the mechanic is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 8. the craftsman house is the librarian##1
 9. the mechanic is in the middle##1
10. the nurse is the person watching action movies##1
11. the cape-cod house is on the right of the futuristic house##1
12. the person watching action movies is on the right of the designer##1
13. the librarian is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5     |
| Color          | aquamarine  | orange     | mauve   | turquise     | azure |
| House         | craftsman | colonial    | futuristic  | cape-cod | townhouse   |
| Job   | librarian        | manager    | mechanic     | designer     | nurse    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific    | documentary | horror | adventure | action   |

