.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-5::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, march, may, august, december
The people use 5 different means of transport: taxi, bike, van, motorbike, scooter
The people have 5 different hobbies: filmmaking, reading, puzzles, fishing, card-games
There are 5 different nationalities: british, french, mexican, thai, nigerian
 1. the french is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the british##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the thai##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is between the french and the person driving the taxi##2
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the mexican##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the mexican##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far right##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
11. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the van##1
12. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
13. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |       2       |       3       |       4       |    5     |
| Birthday   | august       | december       | april   | may      | march    |
| Transport       | scooter | motorbike        | taxi       | van       | bike |
| Hobby        | card-games     | reading        | fishing | filmmaking        | puzzles  |
| Nationality      | thai | mexican | british      | nigerian | french  |

