 3. the accountant is on the right of the journalist##1
 4. the social-worker is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 5. the fan gospel is on the right of the fan house##1
 6. the accountant is between the person who's birthday is in june and the fan pop##2
 7. the fan salsa is the person eating pear##1
 8. the person eating avocado is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
10. the fan classical is on the far right##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who's birthday is in june and the fan pop##2
12. the dancer is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
13. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4    |     5      |
| Job      | journalist  | accountant      | social-worker   | dancer   | police-officer   |
