.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
There are 5 different nationalities: german, canadian, british, italian, thai
House: townhouse, gothic-revival, wooden, craftsman, colonial
The people have 5 different jobs:  photographer, pilot, doctor, freelancer, coach
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: october, november, june, august, january
 1. the coach is between the person who's birthday is in november and the pilot##2
 2. the doctor is on the left of the freelancer##1
 3. the canadian is the craftsman house##1
 4. the german is on the right of the coach##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the canadian##1
 6. the craftsman house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 8. the wooden house is on the left of the canadian##1
 9. the townhouse house is on the left of the wooden house##1
10. the doctor is on the far left##1
11. the person who's birthday is in june is between the doctor and the wooden house##2
12. the italian is on the right of the colonial house##1
13. the british is on the left of the italian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Nationality    | british       | italian    | thai | canadian  | german        |
| House       | colonial | townhouse | wooden  | craftsman | gothic-revival    |
| Job       | doctor        | freelancer   | pilot  | coach   | photographer |
| Birthday   | august       | june      | january      | october | november  |

