.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-18::.
There are 5 different nationalities: indian, pakistani, egyptian, brazilian, colombian
House: gothic-revival, futuristic, ranch-style, colonial, palace
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, dahlia, orchid, rose, sunflower
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: lacrosse, parkour, climbing, tennis, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 2. the colonial house is between the person who growsorchid and the ranch-style house##2
 3. the brazilian is the colonial house##1
 4. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 5. the person who growsbegonia is in the middle##1
 6. the brazilian is between the palace house and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 7. the person who's sport is tennis is the egyptian##1
 8. the indian is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the palace house##1
10. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
11. the ranch-style house is the person who growsdahlia##1
12. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1
13. the colombian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Nationality      | indian      | pakistani         | brazilian      | egyptian | colombian     |
| House           | futuristic | ranch-style | colonial | palace    | gothic-revival  |
| Flower   | rose  | dahlia    | begonia | orchid    | sunflower |
| Sport   | climbing  | parkour        | lacrosse   | tennis    | water-polo     |

