.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-19::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, iris, dahlia, poppy, rose
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, baccarat, pall-mall, game, bluemaster
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, zombie, animation, documentary
The people have 5 different jobs:  lawyer, writer, firefighter, engineer, electrician
 1. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the writer##1
 2. the game-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 3. the person who growsrose is on the left of the electrician##1
 4. the firefighter is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching fantasy movies is between the cain-smoker and the person watching family movies##2
 6. the cain-smoker is on the far left##1
 7. the person who growsdahlia is between the lawyer and the person who growsrose##2
 8. the person who growsiris is between the person who growspoppy and the person who growsbegonia##2
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
10. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
