.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
5 different pets are kept: goat, hedgehog, snake, bike-climbing, ferret
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, havana, tiparillo, montecristo, alhambra
The people use 5 different means of transport: motorbike, car, snowmobile, trike, bike
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, december, august, october, february
 1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
 2. the alhambra-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person driving the bike##2
 3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 4. the alhambra-smoker is the person driving the motorbike##1
 5. the person driving the motorbike is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 7. the tiparillo-smoker is the person driving the trike##1
 8. the owner of the bike-climbing is the person driving the car##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is the person driving the car##1
10. the owner of the bike-climbing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
11. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the havana-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Pet         | snake    | ferret  | hedgehog  | goat      | bike-climbing |
| Cigar   | havana    | alhambra   | montecristo | tiparillo | baccarat   |
| Transport   | snowmobile | motorbike    | bike    | trike       | car         |
| Birthday   | october  | december | february    | august     | april      |

 